{"id":130122,"type":6,"name":"Deadpool","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/69/e8/130122_SB16Y.jpg","rating":{"total":160,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":4,"6":28,"7":77,"8":42,"9":3,"10":3},"score":7.1},"summary":"漫威漫画(Marvel)旗下的著名漫画《X战警》的衍生系列的角色之一，在X战警中数度出场。本名韦德·威尔逊，原本是一个身经百战的特种兵，后来得了癌症，为了获得X战警金刚狼的基因治愈能力才加入“Weapon X”(X武器)计划得以延续生命,电影版预计2016年2月12日登上电影院。\r\n\r\n在原著漫画中，死侍本是个普通人，由于得了不治之症而自愿加入“X武器计划”，他如愿得到了金刚狼自我愈合的能力，但付出的代价是失去了容貌。史崔克将军把他作为失败品投入监狱折磨并继续研究，最终导致他的出逃。死侍是个亦正亦邪的角色，他拥有超人的力量、耐力、速度及自我愈合能力，精通各种武器，擅长搏击术，不过他的精神不太稳定。死侍也是广大漫画迷们喜爱的角色之一。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>死侍</li><li><span>原作: </span>Rob Liefeld、Fabian Nicieza《Deadpool 》、<a href=\"/person/6769\">Marvel Entertainment, LLC</a></li><li><span>主演: </span>Ryan Reynolds、Morena Baccarin、Ed Skrein、<a href=\"/person/36137\">Gina Carano</a>、T. J. Miller</li><li><span>别名: </span>死侍：不死現身</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>惡棍英雄：死侍</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>X战警：死侍</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2016-02-12</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>每集长: </span>1:47:40</li><li><span>首播地区: </span>台灣、香港</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1431045</li><li><span>导演: </span>Tim Miller</li><li><span>制片: </span>Lauren Shuler Donner、Simon Kinberg</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Rhett Reese、Paul Wernick</li><li><span>发行: </span>20th Century Fox</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>20th Century Fox、Marvel Entertainment、The Donners' Company</li>","collection":{"wish":14,"collect":229,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"电影","count":47},{"name":"marvel","count":41},{"name":"漫威","count":25},{"name":"Deadpool","count":16},{"name":"死侍","count":14},{"name":"美国","count":11},{"name":"美漫","count":10},{"name":"科幻","count":7},{"name":"2016","count":6},{"name":"搞笑","count":6},{"name":"欧美","count":5},{"name":"Earth-TRN414","count":4},{"name":"Comic","count":3},{"name":"Ryan_Reynolds","count":1},{"name":"Rhett_Reese","count":1},{"name":"Tim_Miller","count":1},{"name":"Paul_Wernick","count":1},{"name":"战